## Import



Using `pulumi import`, import AWS Chime SDK Voice Profile Domain using the `id`. For example:

```sh
 $ pulumi import aws:chime/sdkvoiceVoiceProfileDomain:SdkvoiceVoiceProfileDomain example abcdef123456
```
